odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 48-A (YRG 48-A), Yale pictorial records and collections.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Yale Alumni Magazine Photographs (RU 694). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: The materials are open for research.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The materials consist of photographs produced for or published in the Yale Alumni Magazine . Included are photographs and artwork for specific articles, camera-ready cover art, and photographs of alumni gatherings and trips. Of particular note are the photographs for the Film Issue, 1968 May, and the May Day Issue, 1970 May.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The photographs are arranged in three series: I. Photographs used in the publication of the Yale Alumni Magazine , 1917-1973. II. Oversize. III. Folio.

userestrict.head: Ownership & Copyright
userestrict.p: Copyright status for collection materials is unknown. Transmission or reproduction of materials protected by U.S. Copyright Law (Title 17, U.S.C.) beyond that allowed by fair use requires the written permission of the copyright owners. Works not in the public domain cannot be commercially exploited without permission of the copyright owners. Responsibility for any use rests exclusively with the user. All copyright requests should be addressed to Yale Alumni Publications, Inc.
